# How to work with assets

## Icons & Images

### SVG Icons

Import SVG files from `@/assets/icons/` using `?react` suffix:

```typescript
import Logo from '@/assets/icons/logo.svg?react';
import SearchIcon from '@/assets/icons/search.svg?react';

// Usage
<SearchIcon />
```

### Images

Import from `public/images/`:

```typescript
// Reference public images directly
<img src="/images/Coin-Logo.png" alt="Logo" />
```

### Lucide Icons

For common icons not in assets:

```typescript
import { Check, Loader2Icon, XIcon } from 'lucide-react';
```
